Ruth?

1064
01:21:44,052 --> 01:21:45,018
We better go.

1065
01:22:29,698 --> 01:22:31,099
You be good.
Okay, pal?

1066
01:22:31,101 --> 01:22:32,133
Okay.

1067
01:22:34,136 --> 01:22:36,337
