1074
01:22:53,023 --> 01:22:54,223
I know so.

1075
01:22:56,693 --> 01:22:57,892
All right, come on.

1076
01:23:04,433 --> 01:23:06,035
Okay.

1077
01:23:06,037 --> 01:23:06,969
I'm just saying goodbye.

1078
01:23:08,104 --> 01:23:09,338
You can't stop me!

1079
01:23:09,340 --> 01:23:11,874
I'm just saying goodbye!

1080
01:23:11,876 --> 01:23:14,243
I know you are, sweetheart.
Let's go back to the car.

1081
01:23:14,245 --> 01:23:16,178
There's nothing we can do.
There's nothing we can do.

1082
01:23:16,180 --> 01:23:18,180
Please reconsider.
Please reconsider!

1083
01:23:18,182 --> 01:23:19,448
There's nothing we can do.

1084
01:23:19,450 --> 01:23:20,449
He deserves better than this.

1085
01:23:21,685 --> 01:23:23,253
Sweetheart, get in the car.

1086
01:23:23,255 --> 01:23:24,988
They don't care about him.
I know they don't.

1087
