They don't care about him!

1088
01:23:37,367 --> 01:23:38,367
Ruth.

1089
01:23:41,272 --> 01:23:42,205
Ruth.

1090
01:23:47,478 --> 01:23:48,411
What was I supposed to do?

1091
01:23:54,118 --> 01:23:56,051
Fight for custody.

1092
01:23:56,053 --> 01:23:58,353
From a half-brother in
small-town North Carolina?

1093
01:23:59,423 --> 01:24:02,025
Come on. We wouldn't have
had a chance!

1094
01:24:02,027 --> 01:24:03,793
And who knows what they
would've done to Daniel.

1095
01:24:06,130 --> 01:24:07,797
We were a family.

1096
01:24:13,404 --> 01:24:15,305
We are a family.

1097
01:24:20,011 --> 01:24:22,179
Ruth, you are my family.

1098
01:24:38,897 --> 01:24:41,332
I wanted kids too, you know.

1099
01:24:52,043 --> 01:24:54,311
We never saw Daniel again.

1100
01:24:57,983 --> 01:24:59,316
Oh, my God.

1101
01:25:54,407 --> 01:25:55,340
Oh, shit.

1102
01:26:04,116 --> 01:26:06,953
<i>Luke Collins is trying
to come around.</i>

1103
01:26:06,955 --> 01:26:11,057
<i>The bull fighter's taking the bull
