1107
01:26:19,334 --> 01:26:21,167
<i>264 on three bulls!</i>

1108
01:26:21,169 --> 01:26:22,635
<i>Luke Collins is your
clear-cut winner.</i>

1109
01:26:27,507 --> 01:26:29,041
He's awesome.

1110
01:26:29,043 --> 01:26:31,577
<i>...number nine spot
in the world.</i>

1111
01:26:37,251 --> 01:26:38,351
Are you okay, Luke?

1112
01:26:40,655 --> 01:26:42,389
I'm fine.

1113
01:26:45,093 --> 01:26:46,426
All right.

1114
01:26:46,428 --> 01:26:49,496
Have an amazing time in New York.
Yes, I will.

1115
01:26:49,498 --> 01:26:50,664
You impressed Adrienne,
you'll impress her team.

1116
01:26:50,666 --> 01:26:52,231
Okay.
Gotta go.

1117
01:26:52,233 --> 01:26:53,566
This is what you've always wanted!
I know!

1118
01:26:53,568 --> 01:26:55,368
Bye! See you on Monday.

1119
01:26:58,206 --> 01:26:59,907
Hey, babe.
I'm walking to the taxi right now.

1120
01:26:59,909 --> 01:27:02,109
<i>Sophia, it's Luiz.</i>

1121
01:27:02,111 --> 01:27:03,310
<i>Hi, Luiz.
Something's happened to Luke.</i>

1122
01:27:09,083 --> 01:27:10,450
Hi, can I help you?

1123
01:27:10,452 --> 01:27:13,020
Um, I need to see
my boyfriend, Luke Collins.

1124
01:27:13,022 --> 01:27:15,122
He came in an ambulance earlier.
I need to see him.

1125
01:27:15,124 --> 01:27:17,025
I'm sorry.
Only family can visit.

1126
01:27:18,460 --> 01:27:20,028
Okay.
Can I at least know how he is?

1127
01:27:21,396 --> 01:27:24,464
His condition is stable,
but he's getting an MRI.

1128
01:27:24,466 --> 01:27:26,199
He took a pretty hard fall.

1129
01:27:26,201 --> 01:27:29,002
If you wanna take a seat,
I'll check with the doctor.

1130
01:27:29,004 --> 01:27:30,270
I'll let you know.

1131
01:27:32,040 --> 01:27:33,173
Thank you.

1132
01:27:39,248 --> 01:27:40,381
So, are you light-headed, dizzy?

1133
01:27:41,350 --> 01:27:42,684
Nausea?

1134
01:27:48,123 --> 01:27:50,590
I'd like you to stay overnight
for observation.

1135
01:27:52,628 --> 01:27:53,995
Sweetie. What are you
doing here?

1136
01:27:54,530 --> 01:27:57,031
I came as soon as I heard.

1137
01:27:58,334 --> 01:27:59,067
Aren't you supposed to
be in New York?

1138
01:27:59,401 --> 01:28:00,668
No, no.

1139
01:28:01,337 --> 01:28:02,303
I should be here.

1140
01:28:05,007 --> 01:28:06,441
Thank God you're okay.

1141
01:28:06,443 --> 01:28:08,109
I'm fine.

1142
01:28:08,111 --> 01:28:09,477
You're lucky to be alive,
is what you are.

1143
01:28:10,447 --> 01:28:12,114
What?

1144
01:28:12,116 --> 01:28:13,449
I just got a little dizzy,
that's all.

1145
01:28:13,451 --> 01:28:15,351
Luke,

1146
01:28:15,353 --> 01:28:17,052
you need to stop downplaying
the severity of your condition.

1147
01:28:18,989 --> 01:28:21,592
If you care about your friend,
you need to make him understand...

1148
01:28:21,875 --> 01:28:24,537
that his riding days are over.

1149
01:28:29,566 --> 01:28:31,667
What is he talking about?

1150
01:28:35,672 --> 01:28:37,639
I'm tired, okay?

1151
01:28:37,641 --> 01:28:39,475
Can we just talk
about it tomorrow?

1152
01:28:41,511 --> 01:28:44,179
Ms. Francis, I am so sorry
about all of this.

1153
01:28:44,181 --> 01:28:48,784
<i>I understand you can't meet the team
this weekend, given the circumstances.</i>

1154
01:28:48,786 --> 01:28:50,486
<i>And I do hope
Luke is okay.</i>

1155
01:28:50,488 --> 01:28:52,321
Yeah, me, too.

1156
01:28:56,493 --> 01:28:58,794
I don't know when I'm gonna
be able to come to New York.

1157
01:28:58,796 --> 01:29:01,663
<i>Oh, really?</i>

1158
01:29:01,665 --> 01:29:04,100
<i>Wait a minute. You're not
rethinking the internship, are you?</i>

1159
01:29:05,636 --> 01:29:07,604
<i>Look, Sophia.</i>

1160
01:29:07,606 --> 01:29:12,308
<i>but you're going to have to figure out
for yourself what that's going to be.</i>

1161
01:29:12,310 --> 01:29:13,743
I know.

1162
01:29:28,359 --> 01:29:30,827
<i>World Finals qualifier from Walkertown,
North Carolina...</i>

1163
01:29:30,829 --> 01:29:33,096
<i>Luke Collins!</i>

1164
01:29:33,098 --> 01:29:35,498
<i>And he is ready
to rock and roll!</i>

1165
01:29:35,500 --> 01:29:37,333
Let's go!

1166
01:29:37,335 --> 01:29:40,371
<i>Luke Collins outside in the middle,
rocked over!</i>

1167
01:29:40,373 --> 01:29:42,306
<i>He is just...
Wow!</i>

1168
01:29:50,282 --> 01:29:53,283
<i>A double flip somersault
face-plant into the dirt.</i>

1169
01:29:56,896 --> 01:29:58,647
<i>You've gotta get him
out of there!</i>

1170
01:30:01,126 --> 01:30:02,493
<i>Yeah,
no doubt about it.</i>

